      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) is maintained under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Version control, regression test suite (450 benchmark cases), and change-control records are documented and available for audit. Achieved level 3 meets the MRL-5 requirement.",
