      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the Navier-Stokes and power-law hemolysis transport equations. Observed order of accuracy 1.97 (theoretical 2.0 for second-order scheme); error norms confirm correct implementation. All verification cases pass at tolerance 1e-4.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
