      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metric is the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH). Validation metric U_val computed per ASME V&V 20; model prediction intervals overlap experimental uncertainty intervals at all five operating points. Validation uncertainty 0.0028 g/100L; model bias 0.0019 g/100L (within validation uncertainty).",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
