        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "QoI relevance acceptance criteria for MRL 5",
        "description": "The validated QoI must be the same quantity used in the regulatory decision (NIH). Surrogate QoI substitutions require documented justification and additional validation evidence."
      }
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
