      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Validation experiments use the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same geometry as the COU device. Blood analog fluid properties match clinical operating conditions. All five COU operating points are included in the validation dataset. No extrapolation beyond validated operating envelope is required.",
