      "rationale": "Iterative convergence verified by monitoring NIH residual to 1e-6 and confirming mass imbalance below 0.01%. Double-precision arithmetic used throughout. Steady-state solution confirmed stable by time-history monitoring over 500 additional iterations after declared convergence.",
