        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Input equivalency acceptance criteria for MRL 5",
        "description": "Computational boundary conditions must be derived from experimental measurements, not assumed. A traceability matrix linking each model input to its experimental source must be documented. Discrepancies between computational and experimental inputs must be within measurement uncertainty."
      }
    }
